Note: Framebuffer Objects

Type GLFramebuffer is Dictionary with:
    framebuffer_id as Integer
    framebuffer_type as GLFramebufferType
    color_attachments as List[GLFramebufferAttachment]
    depth_attachment as GLFramebufferAttachment
    stencil_attachment as GLFramebufferAttachment
    width as Integer
    height as Integer
    samples as Integer
    complete as Boolean
    metadata as Dictionary[String, String]

Type GLFramebufferType is:
    | FRAMEBUFFER
    | DRAW_FRAMEBUFFER
    | READ_FRAMEBUFFER

Type GLFramebufferAttachment is Dictionary with:
    attachment_type as GLAttachmentType
    texture as GLTexture
    renderbuffer as GLRenderbuffer
    mip_level as Integer
    layer as Integer

Type GLAttachmentType is:
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT0
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT1
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT2
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT3
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT4
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT5
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT6
    | COLOR_ATTACHMENT7
    | DEPTH_ATTACHMENT
    | STENCIL_ATTACHMENT
    | DEPTH_STENCIL_ATTACHMENT

Type GLRenderbuffer is Dictionary with:
